<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a2eb9ae-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s7808"><num value="7808">§ 7808.</num><heading> Territorial participation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of State shall ensure participation in the Commission and its subsidiary bodies by American Samoa, Guam, and the Commonwealth of the Northern Mariana Islands to the extent allowed under United States law.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7a2eb9af-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/114/327/tII/s208">Pub. L. 114–327, title II, § 208</ref>, <date date="2016-12-16">Dec. 16, 2016</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/130/1992">130 Stat. 1992</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
